fields.name: Inventory Management System
fields.description:
Inventory Management Project for Microsphere Systems Technology.

This is my second freelance project created with Django, Datatable, and Jquery.

Key Features:

1. Management of Computer Inventory.

2. Historical Data of each row data.

2. Schedule and monitoring of preventive maintenance.

3. Web view for clients.

4. History of changes for units.

5. Email client notification.

6. Generation of reports for PDF and Excel.
